ould get See Hidden I, which keeps the original &quot;Cat &amp; Mouse&quot; game I enjoyed playing before See Hidden/True Sight was ever released. Serious Archer Hunters will spend 9 points for See Hidden II, Which is approximately the same range an Archer can shoot at an Assassin if they had True Sight (maybe you can see the reasoning behind the distances I use now). See Hidden III is powerful as it is now on live, but is now very costly, 19 points. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uwhisperbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whisperbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Student</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#DEB887>(6/30/02 1:57:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fyinyangofcamelotfrm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.users.qwest.net/~whisperbane/images/DAOCPICS/DevIcon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I have a different idea for See Hidden</span><hr size=1> /agree on this one for sure... <p><p><span lang="en-us"><b><font face="Impact">-</font><font face="Verdana"><a href="http://www.users.qwest.net/~whisperbane">Whisperbane</a></font></b><font face="Impact"><br>Deviance - <font color="#FF0000">46th Ranger<br></font>            Demonica - <font color="#FF0000">22nd Nightshade<br></font>Sunniva - <font color="#FF0000">50th Bard<br></font></font></font></span></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/byinyangofcamelot.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=bloodreign>Bloodreign</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Student</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#DEB887>(7/8/02 1:06:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fyinyangofcamelotfrm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=